title: Aljaz Bedene beats Mikhail Youzhny to make last 16 at Shenzhen Open
content: • British No2 eases to 6-3, 6-3 victory over former top 10-ranked player• Bedene will face South Korea’s Chung Hyeon in next round Related: Johanna Konta through at Wuhan Open after Victoria Azarenka retires The British No2 Aljaz Bedene booked his place in the last 16 of the Shenzhen Open with a 6-3, 6-3 win over Mikhail Youzhny.
